name: deepbach
full_description:
DeepBach server from https://github.com/Ghadjeres/DeepBach.

Starts with (no GPU support):

docker run -p 5000:5000 -it --rm ghadjeres/deepbach


Or (using GPU support __requires nvidia-docker https://github.com/NVIDIA/nvidia-docker__):

docker run --runtime=nvidia -p 5000:5000 -it --rm ghadjeres/deepbach
